<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="asleep-adj">asleep <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'sliːp/    美 /ə'sliːp/  </p>
<p>[不用于名词前]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>睡着的；睡熟的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 awake </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>half asleep</strong>
睡眼惺松的</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She is <strong>fast / sound asleep</strong> (= sleeping deeply).
她睡得很熟。</p></div>

<p>注: asleep常用fast, sound修饰，不用very修饰。  </p>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="fall-drop-asleep">fall / drop asleep</h3>
<p>1.<strong>入睡；睡着：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was so tired that I fell asleep the moment my head touched the pillow.
我太累了，头一碰到枕头就睡着了。</p></div></div>